# Assessment Monorepo

A comprehensive monorepo containing a blog application, data table component, and form builder built with modern web technologies.

## Tech Stack

### Core Technologies
- **Monorepo Management**: Turborepo
- **Frontend Framework**: Next.js 14 (App Router)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Testing**: Jest + React Testing Library
- **API**: JSONPlaceholder (mock API)

### Packages
1. **@assessment/core**
   - Shared types and utilities
   - Form field definitions and validation schemas

2. **@assessment/ui**
   - Reusable UI components (Button, Input, Select, etc.)
   - Theme-able components with Tailwind

3. **@assessment/data-table**
   - Feature-rich data table component
   - Built with TanStack Table
   - Supports sorting, filtering, pagination

4. **@assessment/form-builder**
   - Dynamic form generator
   - Supports various field types (text, select, radio, etc.)
   - Conditional field rendering
   - Zod validation integration

5. **@assessment/blog-app**
   - Blog post management
   - Create, read, update, delete operations
   - Infinite scroll pagination

6. **@assessment/services**
   - API service layer
   - React Query hooks for data fetching
   - Centralized error handling

## Setup Instructions

1. **Clone the repository**:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-repo/assessment-monorepo.git
   cd assessment-monorepo
   npm i
   npm run dev

   Then to run any of the app simply serve:
   baseURl/data-table OR baseURl/form-builder or baseURL/blog